Umrla med seksom
Reševalci so truplo 19-letnice ženske, ki je umrla med spolnim odnosom, našli v javni garaži.
05 Nov 2019, 18:32 by T. K.
MAYWOOD – Na noč čarovnic se je 19-letna Francis Victoria Garcia z 21-letnim Michaelom Gaffneyjem, zadeta od še neugotovljenih tablet, v avtu v javni garaži v Maywoodu v zvezni državi New Jersey spravila seksat. On pravi, da se je sredi akcije kar naenkrat onesvestila in rešiti je niso mogli niti reševalci nujne pomoči.Točni vzrok smrti bo znan šele po obdukciji, vendar policisti niso tako zelo prepričani o resničnosti Gaffneyjeve zgodbe, domnevajo namreč, da jo je med grobim spolnim občevanjem zadavil ...

Died during sex
Rescuers found the body of a 19-year-old woman who died during intercourse in a public garage.
05 Nov 2019, 18:32 by T.K.
MAYWOOD - On Halloween, 19-year-old Francis Victoria Garcia and 21-year-old Michael Gaffney, hit by as-yet-unknown pills, have sex in a car in a public garage in Maywood, New Jersey. He says she immediately fainted in the middle of the action and even emergency responders couldn't save her.
